### **PREAMBLE**
The MVG Software License is a free, student-only, copyleft license for software and other kinds of works designed specifically for the TI-84 Plus CE community. 

Most calculator programs are designed to take away your freedom to share or turn them into commercial products. By contrast, the MVG Software License guarantees your freedom — **as a student** — to share and change all versions of the program, while keeping it strictly free, non-commercial, and for students only.

When we speak of “free,” we refer to freedom for students, not price. This License ensures that you have the freedom to distribute copies of MVG OS (gratis only), receive source code, and use pieces of it in new free student programs — provided you are a student and never for teachers or commercial purposes.

