All rights granted under this License are granted only to students. Teachers and school staff have no license whatsoever and are strictly prohibited from using, installing, viewing, or possessing MVG OS in any form.

#### **3. THE “NO-SELL” RULE**
MVG OS is and will always remain 100% free. You may not sell, lease, rent, license, sublicense, or charge any fee (directly or indirectly) for MVG OS or any modified version. Any attempt to do so violates this License and will result in legal action.

