#### **6. CONVEYING VERBATIM COPIES**
You may convey verbatim copies of the Program’s source code to other students only, provided that you conspicuously publish a copyright notice and a copy of this License. You may not receive any compensation.

#### **7. CONVEYING MODIFIED SOURCE VERSIONS**
